ON A CLEAR MATTER, WHOSE NIGHT IS LIKE ITS DAY [WITH RESPECT TO CLARITY]. No ONE STRAYS FROM IT AFTER ME BUT THE DESTROYED ONE.\" .....•.•••••••.•••••••............•.•..••.••••••• 888 RECORDED BY ABU DAAWOOD ... .................................................................................... 889 OTHER POINTS RELATED TO THIS HADITH ......................................................................... 890 SUMMARY OF THE HADITH ............................................................................................ 890 HADITH #29: \"TELL ME AN ACT WHICH ... 11 ................... . . ......................................... . 893 SELECTED VOCABULARY ................................................................................................ 894 TAKHREEJ ................................................................................................................... 895 GENERAL COMMENTS ABOUT THE HADITH ....................................................................... 896 ABOUT THE NARRATOR: MUAADH IBN JABAL .................................................................... 896 \"INFORM ME OF AN ACT WHICH WILL ENTER ME INTO PARADISE AND KEEP ME AWAY FROM THE FIRE.\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 896 \"You HAVE ASKED ABOUT A GREAT MATTER\" .................................................................... 897 \"BUT IT IS EASY FOR WHOMEVER ALLAH, EXALTED BE HE, MAKES IT EASY\" .............................. 898 \"[You SHOULD] WORSHIP ALLAH ... THE HOUSE.\" .............................................................. 899 \"SHALL I NOT INFORM YOU OF THE GATES TO GOODNESS?\" .................................................. 899 \"FASTING [WHICH] IS A SHIELD\" ...................................................................